title: Can't run doccano with docker-compose

I'm trying to run doccano with docker-compose, following that getting-started file: https://github.com/doccano/doccano/blob/master/docs/getting-started.md 

`
docker-compose pull
`
`
docker-compose up
`

and after that doccano_webpack_1 exited with code 1 and with traceback:
